{"tid":229551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"牆後面有貓叫聲，點救佢好","createTime":"2017-05-04T16:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T16:30:02.000Z","uid":92946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73e1b756ffbfc07e0490271b779aa9fdad49a678","tid":229551,"uid":92946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"呢幾日去咗台北旅行，住民宿。咁第一晚都冇咩事，但係去到第二晚，房入面既假牆後面成晚都有貓叫聲傳出，夜麻麻聲到真係嚇到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n去到岩先，玩完返到酒店，又聽到有貓叫聲傳岀，我就估有隻貓仔誤入左啲冷氣機槽入面咁上下。咁我即刻打比民宿個老闆，老闆話聽日中午先黎。<br />\n<br />\n依家都仲有貓叫聲。巴打們，可以點救隻貓好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12efd6a1d97c55ae0f98ce5aaeaf7daafcae604","tid":229551,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:14:52.000Z","msg":"等老板嚟先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重可以點 屌穿牆救貓？"},{"pid":"5fbb7220c2c8baa5a853c8a4a58bfcbf76193da1","tid":229551,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"拆左佢部冷氣"},{"pid":"d5cddaf39ab87dfbb1b17703a3402a8853794773","tid":229551,"uid":22409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:27:03.000Z","msg":"小心 可能唔係貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2dc5497ac6929a9077e935ff99c0ebe01f0a2c","tid":229551,"uid":92946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:30:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小心 可能唔係貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尋日去完猴硐玩完貓黎，唔好嚇9小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}